{"id":31639,"date":"2024-01-13T04:43:00","date_gmt":"2024-01-12T23:13:00","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?p=31639"},"modified":"2023-07-21T11:42:49","modified_gmt":"2023-07-21T06:12:49","slug":"bright-living-room-color-ideas","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/living-room-interiors\/bright-living-room-color-ideas\/","title":{"rendered":"Ditch The Boring &#038; Old With These Bright Colourful Living Room Ideas"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>A neutral palette is always a safe bet but if you\u2019re feeling adventurous, we have the perfect bright colourful living room ideas for you<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Your living room is where you sit down with your family after a day\u2019s hard work, where you rest and repose on holidays, and where you host guests for fun meals and lively conversations. That\u2019s why this one room needs to be all of it \u2013 warm, welcoming <em>and<\/em> cheerful and exciting. One of the best ways to create a space that\u2019s all these and bring out your creative side is to go for bright living room colours. The idea may seem outlandish at first, but we\u2019ve picked some stunning designs that will surely make you fall in love with the idea of a bright and colourful living room. Let\u2019s check them out!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Bring The Space To Life By Adding Pops Of Bright Living Room Colours<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>You might not want to go all out with bright colours in your living room, and that\u2019s completely understandable. But you can still make this room come to life and turn it into a unique, memorable space by adding just a dose of vibrant. A great example is sprinkling pops of yellow across a light-hued room. It works well to make the room look vibrant but at the same time, it isn\u2019t too bright or overwhelming on the eye. The yellow in the pillow, chair and decor make this living room a delight to the eyes. While yellow is a great choice, you can go for any other bright colour like pink or orange that goes well with the overall colour palette of your drawing room.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/11163242\/pop-of-bright-living-room-colour.jpg\" alt=\"Bright living room color with just a dose of vibrant makes the room come to life and make it unique\" class=\"wp-image-31646\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/11163242\/pop-of-bright-living-room-colour.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/11163242\/pop-of-bright-living-room-colour-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/11163242\/pop-of-bright-living-room-colour-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/11163242\/pop-of-bright-living-room-colour-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Break the monotony with pops of yellow<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Enhance your living room's interior design with our solutions!\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/20124603\/enhance-your-living-rooms-interior-design-with-our-solutions.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Bright Colourful Living Room Ideas Are Incomplete Without Colour Blocking<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Using two different colours for your sofa and the wall is a fantastic way to infuse some colour and vibrance into your living room. Coral and dark blue look stunning yet elegant together. While you can choose any suitable combination of colours, if this one impresses you, enhance the room\u2019s look further with some gold furniture, table lamps and planters. Leverage the colour blocking technique in your living room by pairing a soft shade with a bold colour. The softness of coral perfectly complements the dark blue sofa set \u2013 in fact, it even helps tone it down \u2013 and the result is a modern-looking space.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/11163203\/bright-colorful-living-room-ideas.jpg\" alt=\"Bright colorful living room idea with two different colours for the sofa and the wall is a fantastic way to infuse colour\" class=\"wp-image-31641\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/11163203\/bright-colorful-living-room-ideas.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/11163203\/bright-colorful-living-room-ideas-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/11163203\/bright-colorful-living-room-ideas-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/11163203\/bright-colorful-living-room-ideas-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Colour blocking gives your living room a modern look<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Accent Walls Are Popular In Bright Colourful Living Room Ideas<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Neutral-coloured sofas are quite popular when it comes to living rooms designs. But even if you go for sofas of those shades, you can still add some colours and spice to your living room through an accent wall. Creating a bright-coloured accent wall is a superb way to make your living room stand out without going overboard. Just choose a sofa set that\u2019s white, grey, light brown, or of similar tones, go for a bright colour for the wall behind it, and you\u2019ll create a living room that is sure to attract people.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/11163211\/bright-colors-for-living-room-accent-walls.jpg\" alt=\"Bright color for living room walls with neutral-coloured sofa adds the perfect dash of colour\" class=\"wp-image-31642\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/11163211\/bright-colors-for-living-room-accent-walls.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/11163211\/bright-colors-for-living-room-accent-walls-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/11163211\/bright-colors-for-living-room-accent-walls-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/11163211\/bright-colors-for-living-room-accent-walls-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>An accent wall adds the perfect dash of colour<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Also, Read About <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/living-room-interiors\/wall-colour-combination\/\">Wall Colour Combination<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Go Unconventional With Bright Living Room Colours<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>While using teal or related shades in sofas is still common, how often do we think of painting a living room wall teal? Not enough! That\u2019s one thing that certainly needs to change \u2013 given how classy and elegant this teal-coloured living room looks. Team it with some grey furniture, coordinated decor, and add tinges of golden here and there. The final result will be a stunning living room that\u2019ll not only be perfect for everyday activities but also a delight for guests. Other great shades for bright colourful living room ideas are mint green, powder or pale blue, yellow, tangerine, pink and purple. Neutral-coloured curtains in a bright living room are an excellent choice.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/11163226\/bright-living-room-paint-ideas.jpg\" alt=\"Teal bright living room paint idea with grey furniture and tinges of gold here and there lends classy and elegant\" class=\"wp-image-31644\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/11163226\/bright-living-room-paint-ideas.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/11163226\/bright-living-room-paint-ideas-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/11163226\/bright-living-room-paint-ideas-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/11163226\/bright-living-room-paint-ideas-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Teal creates a soothing effect in this living room<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">The Popular Pink And Blue Combination Works Its Magic<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Choosing a soft colour for your wall \u2013 like pink \u2013 and pairing it with a bright sofa and chair set that pops out is a great way to create a colourful living room. Throw in some matching bean bags, cushions, geometric furniture, and decor and the space will become all the more lively and playful.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/11163234\/pink-and-blue-combination-bright-colorful-living-room-ideas.jpg\" alt=\"Bright colorful living room ideas with a combination of pink and blue are great ways to create a colourful living room\" class=\"wp-image-31645\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/11163234\/pink-and-blue-combination-bright-colorful-living-room-ideas.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/11163234\/pink-and-blue-combination-bright-colorful-living-room-ideas-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/11163234\/pink-and-blue-combination-bright-colorful-living-room-ideas-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/11163234\/pink-and-blue-combination-bright-colorful-living-room-ideas-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Pink and blue work together like a charm<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Get a Free Modular Kitchen Worth \u20b92 Lakhs with Your Home Interiors.\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/08183703\/designcafe-offer-free-modular-kitchen-worth-2-lakhs.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Sprinkle In A Bright Colour To Add Some Drama To Your Room&nbsp;<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>If your living room is leaning on the monochromatic side, a bright colour like yellow can be perfect for adding some colour and zing to it. You can add dashes of the bright colour you choose in the TV cabinets, shelves, cushions, window treatments or decor \u2013 the options are endless.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/11163303\/sprinkle-yellow-bright-color-living-room-ideas.jpg\" alt=\"Bright color living room ideas with yellow can be perfect for adding some colour and zing to space\" class=\"wp-image-31649\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/11163303\/sprinkle-yellow-bright-color-living-room-ideas.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/11163303\/sprinkle-yellow-bright-color-living-room-ideas-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/11163303\/sprinkle-yellow-bright-color-living-room-ideas-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/11163303\/sprinkle-yellow-bright-color-living-room-ideas-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Dramatise a subtle palette with a bright shade<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Use Splashes Of Orange To Make Your Living Room Come To Life<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>If your living room is mainly grey or even white, then orange can work like a charm to add some vitality and life to it. Throw in some orange scatter cushions, rugs, and pendant lights, some plants and wooden bookshelves \u2013 and you\u2019ll create a fun and lively living room that excites you and your guests.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/11163256\/splashes-of-bright-living-room-in-orange-color.jpg\" alt=\"Bright living room colors with orange and grey make a charming combination\" class=\"wp-image-31648\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/11163256\/splashes-of-bright-living-room-in-orange-color.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/11163256\/splashes-of-bright-living-room-in-orange-color-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/11163256\/splashes-of-bright-living-room-in-orange-color-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/11163256\/splashes-of-bright-living-room-in-orange-color-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Orange and grey make a charming combination<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Give Your Traditional Living Room A Vibrant Twist<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Even if you want to give your <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/living-room-interiors\/traditional-living-room-designs\/\">living room a traditional touch<\/a>, adding some bright colours in your palette can help accentuate your space and make it like no other. This Moroccan-style living room design skillfully plays with colours, going for blue in the windows and cabinet, orange for the wall, and multicolours for the rug and cushions. The massive plant brings some natural colour and a unique touch to the room.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/11163157\/bright-color-for-living-room-wall-with-a-vibrant-twist.jpg\" alt=\"Bright orange colour for living room wall with blue windows and cabinet brings a traditional touch to space\" class=\"wp-image-31640\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/11163157\/bright-color-for-living-room-wall-with-a-vibrant-twist.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/11163157\/bright-color-for-living-room-wall-with-a-vibrant-twist-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/11163157\/bright-color-for-living-room-wall-with-a-vibrant-twist-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/11163157\/bright-color-for-living-room-wall-with-a-vibrant-twist-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>White furniture comes alive against a bright wall<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Purple And Orange Is A Classic Duo In Bright Colourful Living Room Ideas<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>A list talking about bright colours would be incomplete without mentioning purple and orange \u2013 a bold combination that\u2019s a favourite when it comes to designing interiors. This <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/interior-design\/living-room-design\/\">living room design<\/a> uses orange and purple in just the right proportions, adding life to the room without going overboard with the colours. The wall, painted a different but equally bold shade of purple, is the cherry on the cake.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/11163249\/purple-and-orange-classic-duo-in-bright-colorful-living-room-ideas.jpg\" alt=\"Bright colorful living room ideas add a pop of purple and orange for a royal look\" class=\"wp-image-31647\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/11163249\/purple-and-orange-classic-duo-in-bright-colorful-living-room-ideas.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/11163249\/purple-and-orange-classic-duo-in-bright-colorful-living-room-ideas-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/11163249\/purple-and-orange-classic-duo-in-bright-colorful-living-room-ideas-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/11163249\/purple-and-orange-classic-duo-in-bright-colorful-living-room-ideas-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Bright living room colours for a royal look<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"End to end home interiors solutions for stress free living\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/11\/07152137\/end-to-end-home-interiors-solutions-for-stress-free-living.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>Did these bright colourful living room ideas tempt you to go for vibrant shades in your living room? They certainly made us fall in love with them. But as stunning as bright colours can make your living room look, they\u2019re also risky to use. It\u2019s best to take the help of experts so you can use such bold and unconventional colours to great effect \u2013 which is what we\u2019re here for. Get in touch with our designers and they\u2019ll make your dream 